<title>UK: Ldn gold fix barely changed, platinum moves up.</title>
<headline>Ldn gold fix barely changed, platinum moves up.</headline>
<text>
<p>GOLD - Fixed barely changed at $342.15 from $342.10. Watches platinum for impetus, but any gains seen capped at $345.00.</p>
<p>PLATINUM - Spikes higher on continued concerns over Russian supplies, but seen shaky. Indicated up $2.50 at $380.00/$381.00.</p>
<p>PALLADIUM - Up $4.25 on the back of platinum at $156.50/$157.50.</p>
<p>SILVER - Static at $4.74/$4.76.</p>
</text>
